1. *Milja* je prevelika da bi je mogao preći u jednom danu. (The distance is too great to walk in one day.)

2. Oni se nikada neće pomiriti, iako su razdvojeni samo na *milju*. (They will never reconcile, although they are separated by just a mile.)

3. On je prevazišao svoje *milje* i uspeo da postane najbolji. (He exceeded his limits and succeeded in becoming the best.)

4. Ona je odšetala *milju* i pronašla sebe. (She walked a mile and found herself.)

5. *Milja* nas deli od uspeha. (A mile stands between us and success.)